Vildred.tooltip: Increases basic Speed of other allies, and when the enemy is defeated, launches an extra attack.

Charlotte.tooltip: When attacked, increases Attack and Defense of the caster, and deals great AoE damage to enemies every turn.

Kayron.tooltip: Becomes stronger as the caster's Health gets lower, and upon receiving lethal damage, the caster does not die for 1 turn.

Straze.tooltip: Attacks all enemies, dealing devastating damage to the enemy with the highest max Health.

Krau.tooltip: Increase Defense of all allies and provokes enemy to protect allies.

Violet.tooltip: Has high chance to evade enemy attakcs, and when successfully evading, counterattacks the target.

Diene.tooltip: Supports the battle by increasing Attack and Defense of all allies, Has high Speed.

Command Model Laika.tooltip: Attacks all enemies, putting them to sleep and decreasing Speed. Has very high Speed.

Alencia.tooltip: Dispels all buffs from all enemies, and when using a basic skill, attacks the target with an extra attack, dealing damage.

Choux.tooltip: When using a basic skill, has a chance to attack the target with an extra attack, dealing great damage.

Roana.tooltip: Grants revive to all allies, which allows them to revive with low Health.

Celine.tooltip: When an enemy uses a non-attack skill, instantly deals huge damage against the enemy with the highest Attack.
